### Case 3

```python
n = 999
```

New number

```text
999
```

Sum

```text
27
```

Result

```text
999 × 27 = 26973
```

---

### Case 4

```python
n = 50005
```

New number

```text
55
```

Sum

```text
10
```

Result

```text
550
```

---

# Final Understanding

The algorithm follows this process:

```text
Number
   │
   ▼
Convert to String
   │
   ▼
Visit Every Digit
   │
   ▼
Is Digit Non-Zero?
   │
 ┌─┴─────────┐
 │           │
Yes          No
 │           │
Add to Sum   Ignore
Append Digit
 │
 ▼
Create New Number
 │
 ▼
Multiply New Number × Sum
 │
 ▼
Return Result
```
